- All four engine gates pass (`npm test`, `npm run typecheck`, `npm run lint`, `npm run build`).
- A13 doc updates land in the same commits as the code that introduces each surface.
- Multi-CLI design review and (separately) code review reach convergence Г?" reviewers nitpick rather than catching real issues, per AGENTS.md.
- Branch is rebase-clean against `main` and ready for explicit user merge authorization.
